channel.title: Is it supposed to look like this?
channel.description:
PATH %CommonProgramFiles%\Microsoft Shared\Windows Live;C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_20\bin
CLASSPATH .;C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_20\bin;%CLASSPATH%;C:\Program Files (x86)\Java\jre6\lib\ext\QTJava.zip
And my java is Program Files (x86) should i put that in there to?
